| DAMAGE validate package v1.0

@addfunc+
| password strength check — set @var pw+yourpassword-
| prints: weak / medium / strong
@text+
@text:length+@var/pw-
@var:create+pwlen-
@-
if, (pwlen) < 6
@print+
     +weak-
@-
if, (pwlen) > 5
if, (pwlen) < 12
@print+
     +medium-
@-
if, (pwlen) > 11
@print+
     +strong-
@-
@addfunc:createname"pwcheck"
@---

@addfunc+
| range check — set @var n+(value)- @var min+(min)- @var max+(max)-
| prints: 1 if in range, 0 if not
if, (n) > (min)
if, (n) < (max)
@print+
     +1-
@-
other,
@print+
     +0-
@-
@addfunc:createname"rangecheck"
@---
